resources.string: HUAWEI HiAI encompasses a smart and comprehensive ecosystem based on an innovative \'chip-device-cloud\' three-layer open architecture, enabling developers to quickly and easily use the powerful AI capabilities on Huawei devices, and deliver a next-level smart app user experience.\n\nHUAWEI HiAI Foundation serves as a basic platform providing chip-level capabilities, and a high-performing computing environment characterized by low power consumption and all-scenario versatility, with broad-based support for more than 300 operators and features across the industry.

HUAWEI HiAI Foundation connects smart services and computing chips to provide lightweight model computing capabilities. Supporting interconnection with frameworks such as Huawei MindSpore, TensorFlow, Caffe, Paddle, ONNX and AndroidNN, HUAWEI HiAI Foundation provides for heterogeneous computing of multiple computing units in the chip, and offers efficient tool chains such as model quantization, model conversion, performance optimization, and maintenance and test.
